@baseUrl = https://api-fury.onrender.com
@jobId = takedown-replace-with-returned-job-id

### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Scalar docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

### OpenAPI contract
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

### Create takedown job
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook/violation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adId": "ad_review_001",
  "tenantId": "tenant_review",
  "violationType": "BRAND_VIOLATION",
  "severity": "HIGH",
  "detectedAt": "2026-05-21T14:00:00.000Z"
}

### Idempotency check: send the same adId + tenantId again
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook/violation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adId": "ad_review_001",
  "tenantId": "tenant_review",
  "violationType": "BRAND_VIOLATION",
  "severity": "HIGH",
  "detectedAt": "2026-05-21T14:00:00.000Z"
}

### Get job status
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}

### Invalid payload: Zod returns detailed 400 errors
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook/violation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adId": "",
  "tenantId": "tenant_review",
  "violationType": "INVALID",
  "severity": "HIGH",
  "detectedAt": "not-a-date"
}
